[CAF]

1. Create your account (NO need of French social security):
https://wwwd.caf.fr/wps/portal/caffr/aidesetdemarches/mesdemarches/faireunedemandedeprestation?codeThematique=Logement#DAL
(Choose the option ‘Faire la demande’ -> créer (un compte)

I am not sure it is a good option, but during this CAF account creation process, I chose the option ‘Titre de sejour’ -> my VLS TS visa number.

2. After creating your CAF account, log in using the ´J’ai un identifiant provisoire’ (see the CAF_secondstep.jpeg in this folder). All of the needed info is provided in your email after the CAF account creation.

3. Make the demand 
Log in your CAF account -> choose the ‘Faire la demande’ in this link again:
https://wwwd.caf.fr/wps/portal/caffr/aidesetdemarches/mesdemarches/faireunedemandedeprestation?codeThematique=Logement#DAL

(It will direct us to where to fill in the demand form).

4. To have enough info for the demand in step 3 (relevant to our Montpellier CROUS), please see see the CAF_thirdstep.jpeg in this folder.
